statutory_sections.language:
[HYPOTHETICAL PLACEHOLDER] The Congress finds that:
(1) Renewable energy technologies represent a critical component of national energy strategy;
(2) Regulatory frameworks require updates to accommodate technological advances;
(3) Industry signals indicate market readiness for policy enhancements;
(4) [Additional findings based on approved INTRO_FRAME and INTRO_WHITEPAPER]

[HYPOTHETICAL PLACEHOLDER] The [Agency] shall, not later than [timeframe], update regulations to:
(1) [Specific regulatory update based on policy direction];
(2) [Additional regulatory provisions];
(3) [Implementation requirements]

[HYPOTHETICAL PLACEHOLDER] The [Agency] shall:
(1) Implement regulations in accordance with section 4;
(2) Report to Congress on implementation progress;
(3) [Additional reporting requirements]
